{"_id":"23b3dd25-3639-4525-8066-1e3ae8386338","type":"ability","name":"Work the Crowd","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/influence.svg","system":{"skill":"Influence","name":"Work the Crowd","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You gain a boon on all attempts to influence a crowd, or calm or incite them. So long as a crowd is not actively hostile you can always gain their attention for at least one minute to have your say.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","skill_id":"influence"}}
{"_id":"26c311e4-f776-471c-98aa-1156e824a3c0","type":"ability","name":"Encouragement","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/influence.svg","system":{"skill":"Influence","name":"Encouragement","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"medium","defense":"","target":"Single","range":"Short","duration":"Next","cost":"1","description":"You can encourage your allies in combat. Once before the end of your next turn, you may help them on any check, using Influence to do so. This effect stacks with itself.","roll_type":"help","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"influence"}}
{"_id":"46e7ce51-c8d7-46bb-b863-864dfcc56f60","type":"ability","name":"Mercy","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/influence.svg","system":{"skill":"Influence","name":"Mercy","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"intuition","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"3","description":"When you would apply a wound to an enemy with whom you can communicate, you may use this technique to attempt to have them surrender or flee. You may use this a maximum of once per round. The GM may determine some foes are unwilling to flee or surrender, in which case you are refunded the resources from this technique.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"influence"}}
{"_id":"7eb63501-8f7b-45dd-95e6-cee7b53bfa25","type":"ability","name":"Fitting In","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/influence.svg","system":{"skill":"Influence","name":"Fitting In","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"For the next hour, you can fit in to a particular society or community (such as high society, an undercity neighbourhood, or a criminal society). You are still viewed as an outsider, but are listened to and treated as though you are on equal footing.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"influence"}}
{"_id":"8494fe5f-d2d2-4f63-924c-29c2f9f164c1","type":"ability","name":"Chat Up","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/influence.svg","system":{"skill":"Influence","name":"Chat Up","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"intuition","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"By spending 10 minutes talking to someone, you can make a check vs Intuition. On a success, their attitude toward you is increased, granting you a boon to all positive interactions with them during your current Venture. On a failure, the GM may add a Consequence to the tracker.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"influence"}}
{"_id":"a214222e-6cfc-4687-ae17-baa2b0af1c2a","type":"ability","name":"Keep Them Talking","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/influence.svg","system":{"skill":"Influence","name":"Keep Them Talking","rank":"3","type":"technique","action":"","defense":"intuition","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"You have a knack for keeping people talking. You must have been talking to a subject for at least 1 minute to use this. On a success, they reveal something to you that they did not intend to, such as a secret or incriminating evidence. On a failure, add a Consequence to the tracker.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"influence"}}
{"_id":"ada087a8-ad99-440c-bdc5-2d8df0ed25af","type":"ability","name":"Friends All Around","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/influence.svg","system":{"skill":"Influence","name":"Friends All Around","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You are able to make an additional Connection (increasing your maximum by 1).","roll_type":"none","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","skill_id":"influence"}}
{"_id":"b838db18-9e86-48eb-9ccf-ea8f77f25a52","type":"skill","name":"Influence","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/influence.svg","system":{"skill_id":"influence","domain":"Expertise","rank":1,"stat":"intuition","description":"The Influence skill is used to convince others, whether through diplomacy or intimidation, to see your point of view or do as you suggest. It is primarily used in social interactions."}}
{"_id":"c9c54e43-ef55-4e0c-8b93-98f5c8a19437","type":"ability","name":"Overwhelming Presence","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/influence.svg","system":{"skill":"Influence","name":"Overwhelming Presence","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"3","description":"You may use this ability to gain an Epic Boon on a check made to command, persuade, or intimidate someone into doing what you wish. You also negate any penalties coming from being unmatched in status --- whether that means military strength, social rank, or who currently holds the upper hand.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"influence"}}
{"_id":"d85bb9c8-29be-4643-b093-fedf4608fae4","type":"ability","name":"Smooth Over","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/influence.svg","system":{"skill":"Influence","name":"Smooth Over","rank":"3","type":"technique","action":"","defense":"intuition","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"When an ally fails an influence check, offends someone, or otherwise would risk decreasing someone's attitude toward you, you may attempt to negate the effect. If they have made a check and failed, this allows you to help them retroactively. Otherwise, you make a new check vs Intuition.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"influence"}}
{"_id":"f3e41de7-80cd-4185-99d4-7084e14fe85c","type":"ability","name":"Bully","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/influence.svg","system":{"skill":"Influence","name":"Bully","rank":"3","type":"technique","action":"","defense":"intuition","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"You can make a person who is not actively hostile toward you take an action you want, or agree to something they normally would not, within reason. Add a Consequence to the tracker, even on a success. You can use Strength rather than Intuition as your stat for this check.","roll_type":"","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"influence"}}
